<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Tour Cancelled</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background: #f9f9f9;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .container {
        background: #ffffff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      }
      h2 {
        color: #c0392b;
      }
      .highlight {
        color: #1a73e8;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        background: #1a73e8;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #777;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Important Update</h2>
      <p>Hello {{travellerName}},</p>
      <p>
        We regret to inform you that the tour <span class="highlight">"{{tourTitle}}"</span> 
        with guide <span class="highlight">{{guideName}}</span> at 
        <span class="highlight">{{destination}}</span> has been <strong>cancelled</strong>.
      </p>
      <p>
        Your booking (ID: <strong>{{bookingId}}</strong>) is no longer active.
      </p>
      <p>
        Please visit your bookings page for further details and refund options:
      </p>
      <a class="btn" href="{{link}}" target="_blank">View My Booking</a>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>Journiq Team - Sorry for the inconvenience üôè</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
